@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<style>
    #con{
        background: white;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        width: 80%;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }
</style>
<div class="container mt-4" id="con">
    <h1 id="main" style="text-align: center;">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This policy describes how we collect, use, and safeguard your information.</p>

    <h2>Information Collection</h2>
    <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Personal data (name, email address, etc.)</li>
        <li>Non-personal data (usage data, IP address, etc.)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Use of Information</h2>
    <p>We use the collected information for:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Improving our services</li>
        <li>Communicating with you</li>
        <li>Sending notifications and updates</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Protection</h2>
    <p>We take necessary measures to protect your information from unauthorized access or disclosure.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Request access to your data</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Changes to the Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy from time to time. All changes will be posted on this page.</p>

    <h2>Contact Information</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or suggestions regarding this policy, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:example@example.com">example@example.com</a>.</p>
</div>